# Coffee Shop Website



Welcome to the **Coffee Shop Website** repository! This project represents a modern, visually appealing single-page website for a coffee shop business. It’s designed to showcase the unique offerings and special qualities of your coffee shop to attract customers.

## Features

- **Responsive Design**: Ensures the website looks great on all devices, from desktops to smartphones.
- **Eye-catching Visuals**: High-quality images and modern styling to engage users.
- **Clear Structure**: Easy-to-navigate layout with sections for images, descriptions, and calls to action.
- **Customizable**: Simple HTML, CSS, and JavaScript structure for easy modification.

## Project Structure

```
├── index.html         # Main HTML file
├── css/               # Folder for stylesheets
│   └── style.css      # Stylesheet for the website
├── js/                # Folder for JavaScript files
│   └── script.js      # Main JavaScript file
├── preview.png        # Preview image of the website
├── images/            # Folder for additional images
└── README.md          # Documentation file
```
